# Line-ending policy.
#
# Prisma's migration engine checksums each migration.sql by its raw bytes.
# On Windows, git's core.autocrlf rewrites checked-out files to CRLF, which
# changes those bytes and makes `prisma migrate dev` falsely report a migration
# as "modified after it was applied" (forcing an unwanted dev-DB reset).
# Pin SQL and Prisma schema files to LF on every platform so the checksums
# stay stable regardless of the developer's OS or core.autocrlf setting.
*.sql    text eol=lf
*.prisma text eol=lf
